      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a great source for parts? This vehicle has seen plenty of adventures and is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to life or utilize its components. It's a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast looking for a diamond in the rough at an unbeatable price!",
