    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has been a dependable workhorse over the years. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some suspension work and a thorough tune-up in the near future to keep it on the road reliably. This is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance.",
