      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that defies its tenure. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior appointment reflects meticulous stewardship and zero compromise. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
