    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains preserved. Every surface, from the dashboard to the door cards, is tactilely perfect and free of UV damage. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and features a spotless undercarriage that has never seen salt or snow. This is a rare opportunity to own a time-capsule vehicle for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. All original keys, window stickers, and service records are included for your peace of mind.",
      "price": 43900.0,
